title: GoogleEarth WikiLeaks Mirrors Map [KML]
description:
WikiLeaks currently has well over 1,500 mirrors, which host the same data in different locations in case the parent site is taken down, and one Harvard developer has gathered all of these mirrors into a Google Earth visualization to show from whence these leaks have sprung.  

Full Info: http://www.multigesture.net/2010/12/09/visualizing-wikileaks-mirrors/
